Package fr.sorbonne_u.components.registry.protocol

Interface RequestI

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LookupRequest, PutRequest, RemoveRequest, Request, ShutdownRequest, UnknownRequest
    public interface RequestI
    The interface RequestI declares methods shared by global registry requests.

    Description

    Part of a command design pattern implementation.

    Invariant

     invariant              true
